Well experienced,dedicated, soft spoken doctor i have met ever.
I have met him for arthoscopic surgery on my knee by last month.
He had explained me the issues and and surgery details patiently, gave a good treatment and post surgery recovery support.
I will suggest doctor to my friends and others, if any requirements for ortho medicines and surgery.

Excellent Doctor and great Surgeon. He explained the problem and even the surgery procedure in detail without creating any panic. Has taken extremely good care during surgery and subsequent visits post that. Appreciate his patience in responding to all our questions every time.

He had treated and carried out knee surgery for a sports related injury on my son few years back so we are familiar with the doctor and pleased with his friendliness and his memory to recollect my son's surgery under trying circumstances during the Chennai floods in 2015 ; he even enquired about him and his welfare !

He is very experienced and really confident and soft nature in explaining the problem and solution. Visited twice in last one year and very much satisfied with his approach. I hope he is the chief in Astra for ortho even other ortho specialists in Astra take advice from Dr.Clement. *** ** *** **** ** *** ****** *******

The Dr explained patiently to all the queries raised which will enable the confidence of the patient which is the foremost thing in providing treatment. Further the Dr is so friendly which will enable the patient to reveal the illnesses and also helping to build up confidence on the treatment given at the Centre.
